                    <p class="text-center text-sm-left">Too many ads promise a specific product and then dump the customer on a generic product page. Why lose a customer when they're already showing interest?</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-12 col-md-6 text-container ">
                    <p class="text-center text-sm-left">Instead, First Page creates bespoke landing pages. </p>
                    <p class="text-center text-sm-left">We design a seamless transition, from ad to website to purchase. Our landing page design is laser-focussed on driving home the sale. We don't ask for a hundred things, just one: Buy.</p>
                    <p class="text-center text-sm-left">We make sure your customer always knows where the next step is… It's a yellow brick road all the way to the purchase button.</p>
